Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.25,0:00:17.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯：ひまひま 小約 飯糰粽子   後期：sslish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞了很多彎路呢 我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次能由你來說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.83,0:00:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜歡」這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,430)}說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:24.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(540,430)}不說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,續篇也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個遊戲 下一個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是大拍賣的時候買下的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角色可是遊戲的臉面喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,設計成這樣好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是狗屎遊戲了 這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.62,0:01:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找三葉草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 找到四片葉子的三葉草了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找的是有五片葉子的三葉草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四片葉子的我已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能成為我的葉片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫杉本四葉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,わ~　いい朝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~不錯的早上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.11,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見かける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.11,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寝癖の あの人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貪睡的 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:20.88,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何歳だろう　名前は何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:20.88,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾歲呢？ 叫什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.89,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんか　気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:24.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得 很在意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露 接下來由我來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳能去看看桂馬現在狀況如何嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？神哥哥大人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有去洗澡過的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定又熬夜玩遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不想看見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不可愛的時候真是不想看見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.14,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人 早上了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃早餐了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？找到什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們兩個 早餐還…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼我以前都沒玩這個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來桂木君也走這條路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天鬧鐘壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得比較晚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是明天鬧鐘也壞掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能停在這裡啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾以為沒有命運的邂逅這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在的話 我能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的一舉一動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那略帶憂傷的雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老娘滾出去玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木的妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管好妳哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.97,0:07:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡宅男還是那麼噁心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這才是桂木的作風啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這樣反而更能慢慢享受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 桂木君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後 我能叫你桂馬君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那麼我也叫妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.58,e,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,330)}稱呼她四葉醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.58,e,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,370)}稱呼她四醬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:17.58,e,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,410)}稱呼她小四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳小四可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這個好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 桂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 桂馬君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋炒麵麵包 還剩最後一個喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人到底去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦好啊 人家忘了帶泳衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來已經穿好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人 你讓我找的好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 您是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很中意這遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還沒有玩過關
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這是在以前玩過的所有遊戲裡最貼近我理想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:10:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此為什麼會花那麼長時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴妳一句名言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神作裡的女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是穿越時空的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BY桂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準確的說 應該是能夠超越時空的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是好遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使花點時間來好好享受也是不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要多陪女主角一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會這麼想也是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在玩遊戲所以不能出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人一旦沉迷其中的話就會宅著不出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 難得人家特地跑來一趟的說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像這次特別的著迷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我對此一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是這種感覺的女孩子出場的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的畫畫水平太爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得畫的很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能吧 畫面像是塗鴉的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂馬君 你喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…我也不知道 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道還喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底有多萌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.26,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有啊 畫面這麼差勁的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准侮辱小四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來消息喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊 現在不是做這個的時候
