Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.74,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夾在理想與現實間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:50.27,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:50.27,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一定有一種可以改變世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.84,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:51.84,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:55.14,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:55.14,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走調又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.22,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:57.22,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手繪不佳也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:01.98,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:01.98,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只會為了追尋那唯一的信念而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.63,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.63,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.63,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:03.63,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.97,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“A whole new world god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:06.97,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"一個只有神知道的嶄新的世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.87,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.17,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,440)\fs22}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:09.87,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我將永遠伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:11.17,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs22}我明白你內心受到的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.07,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.87,0:03:13.07,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的騎士 做你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.51,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:14.51,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們會無比閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.06,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:15.06,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.17,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.17,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚 我們將不再懼怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.70,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.17,0:03:19.70,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所謂的“只有神知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.77,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.16,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.77,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:24.16,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這不是現實中的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.87,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.87,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但我會為你做到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.99,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.99,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不管人生將會發生什麼 我都將翻過此頁跨上成人的階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.70,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,441)\fs22}Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.70,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,38)\fs22}記住 沒人可以批判我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:33.02,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Every end leads to a new beginning of the next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:33.02,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終結必將迎來新一幕的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.82,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:35.82,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}度過自己認可的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.45,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.45,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}變的堅強 竭盡所能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.63,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:42.63,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要回頭 繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.93,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Be yourself…Be happy…It's your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:45.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你自己 要開心 因為這是你的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.25,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.25,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:51.34,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Find your love…Find your way…For your life…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:51.34,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為你的人生尋找到愛與歸宿
